  "short_description": "PvEvP 3rd-person extraction-lite action game. Reaching the end of time with companions, explore nine realms suspected in Norse mythology, hunt Vikings, mechas, Valkyries, Tyr, and of course, other players! Capture treasures, evacuate! All items can be traded in free market.",
