  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/961d8228cb137a106d0662cc34e9a603.avif?t=1739504208\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras_big/961d8228cb137a106d0662cc34e9a603.avif?t=1739504208 width=800 height=131 /></span></p></p><br><h1>Official Release</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >December 14, 2024 10:00 AM (UTC+8) Official Release!</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/a69dabaa0598117f1771ae5f0b077005.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/17b54deb3d589f7605d3b13ee40416df.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is inspired by the sci-fi classic <i>Ripples on the Dirac Sea</i> and incorporates the story background of the 1968 Hugo Award-winning novel <i>Lord of Light</i>. It uniquely combines Norse mythology with the quantum physics concept of the \"Dirac Sea\", creating a mysterious and adventurous game world.You will engage in action combat from a third-person perspective, battling fierce enemies such as beasts from Norse mythology, Viking warriors, and Valkyries, with the ultimate goal of successfully escaping with their hard-earned loot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/8063639449631d7464753a27321fd5d9.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game map size 1 km²，Match duration  approximately 10-25 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mode 1: Squad Extraction – A 3-player online PvPvE Tarkov-style looter extraction mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mode 2: Solo Extraction – A solo online PvPvE Tarkov-style looter extraction mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mode 3: Arena 3v3 – A fair 3v3 PvP competitive online mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/93edb0fb09a87aa0072db76cdaba1c97.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.Norse Warrior - Delune (Specialty: Defense/Control; Type: Defensive Melee)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.Norse Berserker - Basaka (Specialty: Charge/Control/Close-Range Damage; Type: Hybrid Melee)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.Nolen Priestess - Skuld  (Specialty: Restricting Enemies/Continuous Damage; Type: Spellcaster Ranged)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4.Elemental Mage - Valfuna  (Specialty: Burst/Area Damage; Type: Spellcaster Ranged)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5.Elven Archer - Fu Yali  (Specialty: Sustained Single-Target Damage; Type: Physical Ranged)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6.Heroic Warrior - Uther (Specialty: Quick Mobility/Healing; Type: Agile Melee)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/affd12c79d819e77fdd977eeae5e8b80.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/75933eb06c6236d066473b843914903d.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/eae665d7ac31202093e6735036eb3671.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/eae665d7ac31202093e6735036eb3671.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/e8b1bed05720ef1e4b3e55942cc423ff.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.Random spawn points, hunt wild creatures and other teams, and engage in PvP to loot equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.Fight against randomly distributed monsters to obtain gear and consumables, as well as crucial hints and clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/bb3516ff5622ecb6bd9483433500a08a.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/bb3516ff5622ecb6bd9483433500a08a.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/bb3516ff5622ecb6bd9483433500a08a.mp4?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the location of the mini-boss, enemies, and the extraction point based on clues. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/5082c76b03131ea61da7ca83b6abdee3.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/5082c76b03131ea61da7ca83b6abdee3.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/fb0ababe9cbae38d35aa2b918fc44d7b.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random small and large bosses. Defeating wild monsters provides clues to mini-bosses and extraction points. Once any team kills a mini-boss, the seal on the large boss is lifted, initiating the ultimate battle!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/258fe05f43708e2187880798a43c3d8e.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/258fe05f43708e2187880798a43c3d8e.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/7d8d8fe6918dad8188734e4634007557.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/7d8d8fe6918dad8188734e4634007557.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/b333c647dd7ab63e41f343772ccb5a5f.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/6cbe813eafa4918d98966f9dcbe5f86c.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can summon your teammates back into the game using a resurrection altar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/92f492d3abbf5f1a3d0d1fa1d69d7d55.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/92f492d3abbf5f1a3d0d1fa1d69d7d55.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/92f492d3abbf5f1a3d0d1fa1d69d7d55.mp4?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/8e6465629255064e51f00abb7c407921.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After defeating a mini-boss and 10 minutes into the match, extraction points will spawn randomly. Players entering different quality extraction points can carry loot with varying value limits, helping them gain an advantage in the next battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/cec62c6165dfe2dd332060b5ecf06389.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/cec62c6165dfe2dd332060b5ecf06389.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/cec62c6165dfe2dd332060b5ecf06389.mp4?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/d72e5aa70897dc13d5f458a9fd9ed047.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/8063639449631d7464753a27321fd5d9.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All items, potions, and equipment can be freely traded among players in the market. Each piece of equipment has a variety of random stats, making every item unique and allowing you to build your own customized setup.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/0ab160b2cfe61d2d030427c43ba1e014.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/0ab160b2cfe61d2d030427c43ba1e014.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/0ab160b2cfe61d2d030427c43ba1e014.mp4?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/53f19991738a977ce45bb3b1bff09ac1.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/d933a785b1608df38a9239b9bbc0cdf7.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/87c7402d65476fd9fcaa8009bf3811f3.avif?t=1739504208\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras_big/87c7402d65476fd9fcaa8009bf3811f3.avif?t=1739504208 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/562f87f35b7341bd0f86ff3b0a2b4217.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The production team has also developed a skin illusion system, where equipment skins dropped in the game allow players to freely trade skins with fiat currency in the Steam Community Marketplace, with out-of-print skins available for each season.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/a93b0d995e2fd8fefa8d06f7218347be.avif?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=836 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/a69dabaa0598117f1771ae5f0b077005.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/17b54deb3d589f7605d3b13ee40416df.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is inspired by the sci-fi classic <i>Ripples on the Dirac Sea</i> and incorporates the story background of the 1968 Hugo Award-winning novel <i>Lord of Light</i>. It uniquely combines Norse mythology with the quantum physics concept of the \"Dirac Sea\", creating a mysterious and adventurous game world.You will engage in action combat from a third-person perspective, battling fierce enemies such as beasts from Norse mythology, Viking warriors, and Valkyries, with the ultimate goal of successfully escaping with their hard-earned loot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/8063639449631d7464753a27321fd5d9.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game map size 1 km²，Match duration  approximately 10-25 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mode 1: Squad Extraction – A 3-player online PvPvE Tarkov-style looter extraction mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mode 2: Solo Extraction – A solo online PvPvE Tarkov-style looter extraction mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mode 3: Arena 3v3 – A fair 3v3 PvP competitive online mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/93edb0fb09a87aa0072db76cdaba1c97.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.Norse Warrior - Delune (Specialty: Defense/Control; Type: Defensive Melee)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.Norse Berserker - Basaka (Specialty: Charge/Control/Close-Range Damage; Type: Hybrid Melee)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.Nolen Priestess - Skuld  (Specialty: Restricting Enemies/Continuous Damage; Type: Spellcaster Ranged)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4.Elemental Mage - Valfuna  (Specialty: Burst/Area Damage; Type: Spellcaster Ranged)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5.Elven Archer - Fu Yali  (Specialty: Sustained Single-Target Damage; Type: Physical Ranged)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6.Heroic Warrior - Uther (Specialty: Quick Mobility/Healing; Type: Agile Melee)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/affd12c79d819e77fdd977eeae5e8b80.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/75933eb06c6236d066473b843914903d.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/eae665d7ac31202093e6735036eb3671.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/eae665d7ac31202093e6735036eb3671.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/e8b1bed05720ef1e4b3e55942cc423ff.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.Random spawn points, hunt wild creatures and other teams, and engage in PvP to loot equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.Fight against randomly distributed monsters to obtain gear and consumables, as well as crucial hints and clues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/bb3516ff5622ecb6bd9483433500a08a.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/bb3516ff5622ecb6bd9483433500a08a.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/bb3516ff5622ecb6bd9483433500a08a.mp4?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the location of the mini-boss, enemies, and the extraction point based on clues. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/5082c76b03131ea61da7ca83b6abdee3.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/5082c76b03131ea61da7ca83b6abdee3.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/fb0ababe9cbae38d35aa2b918fc44d7b.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random small and large bosses. Defeating wild monsters provides clues to mini-bosses and extraction points. Once any team kills a mini-boss, the seal on the large boss is lifted, initiating the ultimate battle!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/258fe05f43708e2187880798a43c3d8e.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/258fe05f43708e2187880798a43c3d8e.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/7d8d8fe6918dad8188734e4634007557.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/7d8d8fe6918dad8188734e4634007557.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/b333c647dd7ab63e41f343772ccb5a5f.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/6cbe813eafa4918d98966f9dcbe5f86c.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can summon your teammates back into the game using a resurrection altar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/92f492d3abbf5f1a3d0d1fa1d69d7d55.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/92f492d3abbf5f1a3d0d1fa1d69d7d55.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/92f492d3abbf5f1a3d0d1fa1d69d7d55.mp4?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/8e6465629255064e51f00abb7c407921.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After defeating a mini-boss and 10 minutes into the match, extraction points will spawn randomly. Players entering different quality extraction points can carry loot with varying value limits, helping them gain an advantage in the next battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/cec62c6165dfe2dd332060b5ecf06389.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/cec62c6165dfe2dd332060b5ecf06389.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/cec62c6165dfe2dd332060b5ecf06389.mp4?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/d72e5aa70897dc13d5f458a9fd9ed047.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/8063639449631d7464753a27321fd5d9.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All items, potions, and equipment can be freely traded among players in the market. Each piece of equipment has a variety of random stats, making every item unique and allowing you to build your own customized setup.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/0ab160b2cfe61d2d030427c43ba1e014.poster.avif?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/0ab160b2cfe61d2d030427c43ba1e014.webm?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/0ab160b2cfe61d2d030427c43ba1e014.mp4?t=1739504208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/53f19991738a977ce45bb3b1bff09ac1.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/d933a785b1608df38a9239b9bbc0cdf7.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/87c7402d65476fd9fcaa8009bf3811f3.avif?t=1739504208\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras_big/87c7402d65476fd9fcaa8009bf3811f3.avif?t=1739504208 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/562f87f35b7341bd0f86ff3b0a2b4217.webp?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=36 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The production team has also developed a skin illusion system, where equipment skins dropped in the game allow players to freely trade skins with fiat currency in the Steam Community Marketplace, with out-of-print skins available for each season.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421650/extras/a93b0d995e2fd8fefa8d06f7218347be.avif?t=1739504208\" width=800 height=836 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
